  "2026-05-14T06:51:10.044Z",codex-package-refactor,"Implementation update: added packages/pm-calendar with TypeScript-authored extension entry/runtime plus checked-in JS artifacts, exposed calendar runtime helpers through the public SDK barrel, updated first-party package catalog/install-all tests, and fixed package output service handling so installed calendar preserves markdown default output. Verification passed: pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/package-manifest.spec.ts tests/unit/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts tests/unit/builtin-extension-entrypoints.spec.ts tests/unit/calendar-command.spec.ts (80 tests)."
  "2026-05-14T06:52:46.381Z",codex-package-refactor,"Manual temp-project evidence: isolated PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH smoke passed with node dist/cli.js init, install calendar --project, package catalog (total 4 with calendar installed), create item with deadline/reminder, calendar markdown output, cal --json structured output with 2 events, contracts --command calendar --runtime-only --availability-only, and health --check-only clean in the sandbox."
  "2026-05-14T07:02:38.847Z",codex-package-refactor,"Continuation 2026-05-14: refreshed bootstrap from current checkout, confirmed existing calendar extraction changes and package-first lineage, and launched read-only sub-agent audits for CLI surface, SDK preservation, and package/dogfood/observability coverage before finalizing this slice."
  "2026-05-14T07:07:34.845Z",codex-package-refactor,"Contract cleanup update: static SDK actions no longer advertise package-owned calendar/templates actions; installed pm-calendar still exposes calendar dynamically through runtime-only contracts. Verification passed: pnpm typecheck; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts tests/unit/calendar-command.spec.ts tests/unit/templates-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts (127 tests)."
  "2026-05-14T07:09:43.217Z",codex-package-refactor,"Packed smoke hardening: scripts/smoke-npx-from-pack.mjs now verifies the packed CLI in an isolated temp project with init, install all, package catalog, calendar command execution, and upgrade --packages-only --dry-run. Verification passed: pnpm smoke:npx."
  "2026-05-14T07:23:28.668Z",codex-package-refactor,"Release gate evidence: node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --telemetry-mode required --max-sentry-critical 10 --max-sentry-high 20 --max-telemetry-error-rate 10 --json passed. Gate covered build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, 100% coverage, version policy, secret scan, packed npx package smoke, npm pack dry-run, compatibility, and Sentry/telemetry. Observability summary: Sentry access ok with 1 critical/4 high under thresholds; telemetry required mode ok with finish_error_rate_pct 2.4 and zero failures missing error codes."
  "2026-05-14T07:25:45.438Z",codex-package-refactor,"Docs cleanup: consolidated duplicated docs/SDK.md content and documented the static core action versus runtime package action contract split for package-owned actions such as calendar and templates. Verification passed: node scripts/release/docs-skills-gate.mjs."
